{"tid":158083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：可留多久就留多久","createTime":"2017-03-16T04:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T14:09:00.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56102e2acb138512e7a0f609e9269b45005c5761","tid":158083,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"在歐聯被大炒出局後，阿仙奴領隊雲加備受壓力，更有球迷抗議要求他離隊，不過在周六領軍殺入英足盃4強後，雲加坦言仍會長期留隊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然對手只是非聯賽球隊林肯城，但強陣並有主場之利的阿仙奴也要戰至上半場補時階段才開紀錄，幸最終仍大勝5:0。雲加（Arsene Wenger）坦言球隊經過近期慘淡的戰績後，有一點信心危機。<br />\n<br />\n雲加說：「不過在下半場，球員的自信回來了。外界都有很多意見，但不代表他們的說話都是對的。我們要在場上證明我們的價值。」同時，他又大讚林肯城甚有組織，而且目標十分清晰。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴球迷賽前高舉寫上&ldquo;Wexit&rdquo;標語，促請雲加下台。這名詞顯然是借用&ldquo;Brexit&rdquo;，即英國脫歐的縮寫。對於球迷的抗議，雲加淡然表示：「我在過去已證明了，我對這家球會百分百地付出，可以留隊多久，我就留多久。我只會專注工作，任其他人去評論我的表現。」"},{"pid":"8f1012cf96fbe2f8c5f177975603add5dbe885c4","tid":158083,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"反雲又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb556996ba72d5437449cf3cbdba01aacf13b6d","tid":158083,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T04:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雲加心理素質好高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43af97c15ef99b4da1ab05d8e5f53bf836e8cd1f","tid":158083,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:09:51.000Z","msg":"屌極都唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f67803caab384ff6d9194c6322b3aa4a2f6e43","tid":158083,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"一萬年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e7720e77668e07f619574072b32f95f6d2228a","tid":158083,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"教到死"},{"pid":"c493b265232e1e16d8c0be77e4240f610cfeb7ea","tid":158083,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教到死</blockquote><br />\n來簡約地教多80年<br />\n態度未曾改變"},{"pid":"0326aafc4fb7098e58aefe902f4aa539434a7d20","tid":158083,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"請珍惜雲加<br />\n反雲仆街死"},{"pid":"ec8d32c8fcd68b3a785e0bbc3e06a4a3758dcd20","tid":158083,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"雲加專一至死 不理會路斯基<br />\n從西甲入手未 但後防唔爭氣<br />\n若靠基佬和藍斯爭逐遊戲"},{"pid":"892677bb02cb8f0525583bd878f1bc81018ac798","tid":158083,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請珍惜雲加<br />\n反雲仆街死</blockquote><br />\n樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61faed96f97e282d7adfcce197de47992af415b6","tid":158083,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"雲與阿永不可別離<br />\n教佢教到死 ～～～ E Yeah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13da5fe37aad27f93cff02bddda23a4df96218f6","tid":158083,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8db3a1f9ff53c23d4b957cbba2c906affbe896a9","tid":158083,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"603d98db1a819339da71866105aaca5378a82061","tid":158083,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc